Device: Raspberry Pi 3
OS: Raspbian

Emissary is a Linux/Apache/MySQL/PHP server. It also hosts an SSH connection for
remote administration and is the principle public-facing device in the topology.

Access Restrictions:
    Accessible only from within the LAN. 

Special Software:
    OSSEC Client
    ModSecurity Web Application Firewall (configured to interface with OSSEC)
    Apache
    WordPress
    SMTP: postfix
    NoIP Dynamic DNS Client